        <h2>About Us</h2>
        <p>Pacific Northwest National Laboratory (PNNL) is a world-class research institution located in the Pacific Northwest region of the United States. We are dedicated to advancing scientific discovery and innovation to address some of the most challenging problems facing our nation and the world.</p>
        
        <h2>Our Mission</h2>
        <p>Our mission is to strengthen the United States' scientific foundations and innovation to drive economic growth, enhance national security, and improve quality of life. We conduct research in a wide range of areas, including energy, environment, national security, and fundamental sciences.</p>
        
